{"link":"https://trailhead.salesforce.com/en/modules/get_ready_for_dreamforce_become_salesforce_speaker/units/get_ready_for_dreamforce_sf_speaker_build_persuasive_demo","title":"Build a Persuasive Demo Unit | Salesforce Trailhead","shortLink":"get_ready_for_dreamforce_sf_speaker_build_persuasive_demo","questions":[{"title":"1What is the main reason to include a demo in your presentation?","answers":[{"content":"A People learn from a demo because they can see how something is actually done.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"}],"wrongAnswers":[{"content":"B Demos prove you are the top expert in your field.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(3)"},{"content":"C All topics are boring without a demo.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(4)"},{"content":"D Demos are the the only way to have interaction with your audience.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"}],"correctAnswer":{"content":"A People learn from a demo because they can see how something is actually done.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"},"selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1)"},{"title":"2What should you do when demoing technology during a presentation?","answers":[{"content":"B Make sure that all demos are connected by a coherent storyline.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(3)"},{"content":"C If you use a story, try to include characters and situations your primary audience will relate to.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(4)"},{"content":"D Never include a story as part of a demo. Just show the technology.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"}],"wrongAnswers":[{"content":"A Make sure each demo is independent of the others.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"}],"correctAnswer":{"content":"C If you use a story, try to include characters and situations your primary audience will relate to.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(4)"},"selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2)"},{"title":"3Which of the following steps are important when preparing your technology for a demo?","answers":[{"content":"B Keep things fresh and improvisational by creating a demo on the fly during the presentation.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(3)"},{"content":"C Always use both Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience in demos.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(4)"},{"content":"D Take screenshots of key screens in case something goes wrong and your demo doesn\u0027t work.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"}],"wrongAnswers":[{"content":"A Use as many devices as you can within each of your demos.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"}],"correctAnswer":{"content":"D Take screenshots of key screens in case something goes wrong and your demo doesn\u0027t work.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"},"selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3)"}]}